{"tid":2496074,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈少年團聯名麥當勞推「BTS套餐」　附特殊醬…發行名單有台灣！","createTime":"2021-04-19T14:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T18:03:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":118,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1530622dc40b89af99bcadd1ac98c708f6afe0","tid":2496074,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"南韓天團防彈少年團（BTS）影響力遍及全球，在全世界都有大批粉絲支持，更為KPOP寫下許多世界第一的紀錄，19日更公開一項超狂聯名，那就是與全球知名的速食餐廳麥當勞合作，推出「BTS套餐」並附上特殊醬料，即將在全球將近50個國家發行，其中還包含台灣，火速引起大批網友熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5575/5575684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5575%2F5575684.jpg&h=405fb192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團將與麥當勞合作。（圖／翻攝自Twitter／@BTS_twt）<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞19日在官方推特宣布，即將在5月發行「BTS套餐」，更曬出一張以薯條拼成的防彈少年團Logo，底下的金色拱門符號旁還寫著BTS字樣，接著更公開了一張發行國家的圖表，可以看到美國、加拿大、巴西、馬來西亞等地都將在5月26日發行，而南韓則是在5月27日推出，仔細一看名單中也有出現台灣字樣，將在6月9日上市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5575/5575682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5575%2F5575682.jpg&h=8630b815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲麥當勞發行「BTS套餐」，將在全球將近50國家上市。（圖／翻攝自Twitter／@BTS_twt）<br />\n<br />\n根據韓媒《Digital Times》報導，BTS套餐中將會有防彈少年團成員喜歡的麥克雞塊、薯條，並附上特殊的甜辣醬與美式海鮮醬（Cajun Sauce），最後配上飲料，BTS更「獻聲」為麥當勞演唱了招牌音效，這一個超狂消息一出後，立刻引爆熱烈迴響，歌迷紛紛留言「我還不吃爆」、「吃起來阿米們」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5575/5575681.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5575%2F5575681.jpg&h=08bfbff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲麥當勞發行「BTS套餐」，餐點中會附上特殊醬料。（圖／翻攝自Twitter／@BTS_twt）<br />\n<br />\n此外，在麥當勞公開的發行國家中，有眼尖的網友發現並沒有出現中國，因此消息傳到微博後，也引起大陸網友討論，留言「竟然沒有大陸」、「哭了，為啥其他地方都有」，更有民眾喊話「金拱門你別不知好歹」，吐槽「薯條會不會就7根」，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港有<br />\n姜濤OUT!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"05ccf4b70642024cf94a44a47c71ebc99bafb9ab","tid":2496074,"uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFjVD7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFjVD7d.jpg&h=4951f6ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43ae80c67f6cb2ca474811812e100ffb43b32f54","tid":2496074,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"麥當奴需要人!!!!"},{"pid":"27822302ad48e935dd863a356b530091ee16d3b6","tid":2496074,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"我一定要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"6c9e264ef4dc488114ccf85bb802d398f7ef6cc0","tid":2496074,"uid":274500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"bts嘅特殊醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267e8f7286f8228f8380875659813f28dd05c60b","tid":2496074,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ea940241c57b826adee649abcede5e32f2dd02","tid":2496074,"uid":123303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4f7d5ec09d8e674b011675acd9cf120199b21f","tid":2496074,"uid":312758,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"BTS白汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ff4e11026abbe3c184e4d2599d2d41651da2ae","tid":2496074,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27822302ad48e935dd863a356b530091ee16d3b6","tid":2496074,"uid":256952,"l